23852.title: Metallica Presents: Helping Hands Concert
23852.description: See Metallica in a unique performance at the Microsoft Theatre in Los Angeles. Benefiting their All Within My Hands Foundation, the Helping Hands Concnert honors AWMH's partners in its efforts to help those in need in communities around the world that have supported the band.
